T02D3365:41b-1: a'arya dz'ang+gu l'i s'a dha nam /
T02D3365:41b-3: 'phags ma dug sel ba'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3365:41b-4: 'phags ma dug sel ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3365:41b-5: sngon du bstan pa'i cho ga nyid //
T02D3365:41b-6: rang snying dmar po dkyil 'khor la //
T02D3365:41b-7: dz'am gi ye shes las rdzogs pa'i //
T02D3365:41b-8: dug sel zhes pa'i rig ma ni //
T02D3365:41b-9: ser po'i gdengs ka bdun gdengs shing //
T02D3365:41b-10: 'bar zhing g-yo ba'i nor bus brgyan //
T02D3365:41b-11: zhal gsum dang ni spyan gsum ste //
T02D3365:41b-12: gzhon nu ma yi phyag gsum 'bar //
T02D3365:41b-13: khros pa dang bcas dgod pa nyid //
T02D3365:41b-14: sbrul gyi rgyan gyis ske rags byas //
T02D3365:41b-15: phyag drug rol pas gnon pa ste //
T02D3365:41b-16: mi bskyod dbu la nye bar bzhugs //
T02D3365:41b-17: g-yas kyi phyag na rdo rje ste //
T02D3365:41b-18: gnyis pa dag ni ral gri 'phyar //
T02D3365:41b-19: gsum pa gar tshul mda' bsnams pa //
T02D3365:41b-20: g-yon na sdigs mdzub zhags pa ste //
T02D3365:41b-21: gnyis pa dag ni me tog go //
T02D3365:41b-22: gsum pa'i phyag na gzhu bsnams so //
T02D3365:41b-23: me tog gis brgyan ska rags te //
T02D3365:41b-24: padma'i gdan gnas gser gyi mdog /'od ni dmar po'i dkyil 'khor ro //
T02D3365:41b-25: dbang po'i gzhu ni 'phro zhing sbrul //
T02D3365:42a-2: sangs rgyas gzugs ni 'phro ba ste //
T02D3365:42a-3: zla bum rang gi phyag na'o //
T02D3365:42a-4: dug gis brgyal ba dbang bskur zhing //
T02D3365:42a-5: dz'am gis kha ni brgyan par bsgoms //
T02D3365:42a-6: dug ni med na sku gsum gyis //
T02D3365:42a-7: dug sel rtag tu bsgom par bya //
T02D3365:42a-8: de ltar 'di yis bsgoms bzhin pa //
T02D3365:42a-9: ring po mi thogs byang chub 'thob //
T02D3365:42a-10: lag pa gnyis kyis sprul gyi gdengs ka'i rnam pa yis /
T02D3365:42a-11: spyi bor gdengs ka gdugs lta bur byas pa ni dug sel ma'i phyag rgya ste /
T02D3365:42a-13: aom na ma:sha ba ra ku m'a r'i ye tsur tsa ts'a la ya tsur ts'a la ya /
T02D3365:42a-14: sam gha ta ni matta ma tam gi aa hang bidbhe aa he /
